<HEADLINE> Cos., Individuals in SEC Fraud Case </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	The Securities and Exchange Commission announced enforcement  
actions Tuesday alleging accounting fraud against these companies 
and individuals. Those agreeing to settlements neither admitted nor 
denied wrongdoing: 
</P>
<P>
	--Mitchell C. Kahn, president and chief executive officer, First  
Merchants Acceptance Corp., Deerfield, Ill.; Paul M. Van Eyl, vice 
