<HEADLINE> MLS Board Discusses Changes </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	DENVER (AP) -- Major League Soccer's board of directors said  
Tuesday a number of changes will be announced after November's 
championship game. 
</P>
<P>
	``There are no changes we can discuss at this point. We made  
some recommendations as it relates to rule changes, our schedule, 
our future on television, and our thoughts about expansion,'' newly 
